"""MAD-based outlier rejection + maxlift clamp.

For each subject, compute per-tile z_q. Across tiles, find robust lower bound
on tile_z (median - k*MAD). Reject tiles whose z is below this bound (they're
autofluorescence-contaminated). Then compute max lift over remaining tiles.
"""
